seed.description: Value to seed the Faker generator for deterministic output: https://faker.readthedocs.io/en/master/#seeding-the-generator

locale.description: One or more LCID locale strings to produce localized output for: https://faker.readthedocs.io/en/master/#localization

faker_config.description: Config for the [`Faker`](https://faker.readthedocs.io/en/master/) instance variable `fake` used within map expressions. Only applicable if the plugin specifies `faker` as an addtional dependency (through the `singer-sdk` `faker` extra or directly).
